{"tid":1289593,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港真正需要嘅唔係一個梁天琦","createTime":"2019-07-06T07:18:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T08:35:56.000Z","uid":266134,"like":84,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4b600ab694c652a1072adfacd9db98fedead1a24","tid":1289593,"uid":266134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:18:43.000Z","msg":"近期反送中運動令好多和理非𨍭為勇武，所以多咗人話掛住梁天琦，當年跟唔切而對唔住佢。我都好掛住。<br />\n<br />\n但有人話等佢出嚟帶領香港人，不敢苟同。我哋應以最好嘅香港迎接天琦，即使唔成功，都要以自身最佳狀態表示聽我哋準備好。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港真正需要嘅係每一個香港人，<br />\n而我哋每一個人都要成為梁天琦。<br />\n</span></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P6JEEm6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP6JEEm6.png&h=43e25f78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後容我重申五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選"},{"pid":"b8b54860d48edc34dd01547e1c38eca99d5bdfee","tid":1289593,"uid":266134,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:19:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g4kLzV0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg4kLzV0.png&h=e68f2368&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc0ffec7a78a403e56918d49faf1965de0058f6d","tid":1289593,"uid":161099,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:25:09.000Z","msg":"我都好掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a4d2588c199e7c1c45a14f154a4e0d16a2658fd","tid":1289593,"uid":262618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:25:53.000Z","msg":"唔推唔係人"},{"pid":"0b4f5bff496f579fbbcd24cc5a412693b81e23fe","tid":1289593,"uid":195485,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:26:08.000Z","msg":"佢已經踏出咗最重要嘅第一步 我哋要做嘅就係跟上佢 甚至超越佢"},{"pid":"2429e2c27c794e9262be11611ed7ee6167fd417d","tid":1289593,"uid":11149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:26:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ad0c7fb36ef164e4a9161c458d9de82bd824d2","tid":1289593,"uid":136803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:27:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c18ec041c446817100635e030343afe4a1801315","tid":1289593,"uid":30146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:28:19.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講！"},{"pid":"f2a6e7050ddfed2bfeda01a7dcd35b7ae891e4bb","tid":1289593,"uid":71459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:30:57.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"640225b88924d8e7dd069583c60d8d8967248d6f","tid":1289593,"uid":60260,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:31:35.000Z","msg":"天琦幫我地開左個頭<br />\n我地要幫佢寫返個最好既結局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34d36f15907c370ecad79efb96084b88720b2bec","tid":1289593,"uid":84975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:35:07.000Z","msg":"我們都是梁天琦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf96e238325384e676c7777845f14d8b9344ce4","tid":1289593,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:35:16.000Z","msg":"佢出返黎都唔好俾佢擔大旗啦<br />\n佢而家咁撚出名,出返黎如果再咁高調<br />\n一定極速俾人斬首行動再拉返入去嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出返黎都係幕後講下野好啦"},{"pid":"f998e933c8e072210c04610874d274cadeade4cb","tid":1289593,"uid":93350,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:35:38.000Z","msg":"梁天琦代表既係一個理念<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00e8747daa9b9911706f0722166e2ebaf9edda1e","tid":1289593,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T07:36:30.000Z","msg":"如果每日落嚟嗰150個係武漢人<br />\n香港應該獨立咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />